metadata.name: Salt
metadata.description:
September 2019 I was awarded the opportunity to live in Iceland for one month as an Artist in Residence at a small working farmhouse in the remote Westfjords. I spent my time photographing the land and the family's winter Shepherding and Mussel processing operations with two other artists also from California.

Salt used as a de-icer for roadways in inclement weather Reykh√≥lareppur, Iceland.
